      536.82,
      522.62,
      577.73
    ],
    "text": "Both the rider and the pillion passenger, who sustained severe injuries, later died after being admitted to the Dharmapuram Hospital. The deceased were residents of the Dharmapuram area and were in their twenties.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
